abstract: Minnesota Vikings trade quarterback Matt Cassel to Buffalo Bills for two undisclosed draft picks; other NFL news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Minnesota Vikings and the Buffalo Bills agreed on a trade that will send Cassel to the Bills and fetch the Vikings two undisclosed draft picks.

headline.main: Vikings Send Matt Cassel to Bills

snippet: The Minnesota Vikings and the Buffalo Bills agreed on a trade that will send Cassel to the Bills and fetch the Vikings two undisclosed draft picks.
